CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 3, 1962, pg. C3, reads: "Photos of Your Pittsburgh Story Rally - Speaker's Platform - Shown on the speakers' platform are (left to right): William C. Page, who made the award presentation; Dr. W. Roderick Brown, winner in field of medicine; P. L. Prattis, who introduced the Right Rev. Joseph Gomez, AME Bishop who's seated next to Mr. Prattis; Mrs. Robert L. Vann, Courier president-treasurer..."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of William C. Page, Dr. W. Roderick Brown, P. L. Prattis, Bishop Joseph Gomez, and Jessie Vann, with Bill Nunn Sr. in center of second row, seated on stage in Soldiers and Sailors Memorial Hall, for Pittsburgh Courier Newspaper's Appreciation Day Rally
